<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Name - Academic Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-primary: #ffffff;
            --bg-secondary: #f8f9fa;
            --text-primary: #2c3e50;
            --text-secondary: #5a6c7d;
            --accent: #3498db;
            --accent-hover: #2980b9;
            --border: #e1e8ed;
            --highlight: #fff9e6;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        section {
            scroll-margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .hero {
            padding: 60px 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .profile-photo {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 3px solid var(--border);
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .bio {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .btn-social {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .btn-social:hover {
            color: white;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-social-text {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .btn-social-text:hover {
            color: white;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .sr-only {
            position: absolute;
            width: 1px;
            height: 1px;
            padding: 0;
            margin: -1px;
            overflow: hidden;
            clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
            white-space: nowrap;
            border-width: 0;
        }

        section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        section:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        #news-list {
            max-height: 200px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 10px;
        }

        #news-list::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        #news-list::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        #news-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--border);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        #news-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .news-item {
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .news-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .news-date {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .filter-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .filter-btn {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .filter-btn:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .filter-btn.active {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .publication {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
            padding: 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .publication:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .publication.highlighted {
            background: var(--highlight);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .pub-image {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 6px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .pub-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .pub-title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .pub-authors {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .pub-authors .me {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .pub-venue {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .award-text {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .pub-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .pub-link {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .pub-link:hover {
            color: var(--accent-hover);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .pub-link::before {
            content: "[";
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .pub-link::after {
            content: "]";
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .prospective-students {
            padding: 30px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .prospective-students p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .prospective-toggle {
            color: var(--accent);
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .prospective-toggle:hover {
            color: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        .prospective-content {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .prospective-content.show {
            display: block;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .social-links {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .profile-photo {
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .publication {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .pub-image {
                width: 100%;
                height: 200px;
            }

            nav {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <nav>
                <a href="#about">About</a>
                <a href="#news">News</a>
                <a href="#publications">Publications</a>
                <a href="#mentoring">Mentoring</a>
                <a href="#teaching">Teaching</a>
                <a href="path/to/your-cv.pdf" download>CV</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="hero" id="about">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Profile Photo" class="profile-photo">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Your Name</h1>
                <div class="title">Assistant Professor • Computer Science • University Name</div>
                <div class="bio">
                    <p>I am an assistant professor in the Department of Computer Science at University Name. My research focuses on machine learning, computer vision, and artificial intelligence. I am particularly interested in developing methods that enable machines to learn from limited data and generalize to new domains.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Previously, I completed my PhD at Another University, where I was advised by Professor Smith. I also spent time as a research intern at Tech Company Lab.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 12px;"><strong>Email:</strong> yourname [at] university [dot] edu</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="social-links">
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-social"><span class="sr-only">Google Scholar</span><i class="fa fa-graduation-cap"></i></a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-social"><span class="sr-only">GitHub</span><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-social"><span class="sr-only">Twitter</span><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-social"><span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="prospective-students">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-primary);">Research</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
                    My research focuses on enabling machines to learn efficiently from limited data and adapt to new environments. I work at the intersection of machine learning, computer vision, and artificial intelligence, with particular emphasis on few-shot learning, meta-learning, and domain adaptation. I'm interested in developing methods that can generalize across diverse visual domains and require minimal human supervision.
                </p>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 10px;">
                    Currently, I'm exploring how neural networks can acquire new visual concepts from just a handful of examples, and how we can build systems that maintain performance when deployed in novel, real-world scenarios.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                <strong>Dear prospective students:</strong> <span class="prospective-toggle" onclick="toggleProspective()">Click here</span> for information.
            </p>
            <div id="prospective-content" class="prospective-content">
                <p>Thank you for your interest in working with me! I am always looking for motivated students to join my research group.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>For PhD applicants:</strong> Please apply through the formal admissions process at University Name. Feel free to mention my name in your application if you're interested in working with me. Due to the high volume of emails, I may not be able to respond to individual inquiries, but I carefully review all applications that list me as a potential advisor.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>For current students:</strong> If you're already at University Name and interested in research opportunities (independent study, MS thesis, undergraduate research), please email me with your CV, transcript, and a brief description of your research interests. I typically have openings for 1-2 students per semester.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Research areas:</strong> My group works on machine learning, computer vision, and AI. We're particularly interested in projects involving few-shot learning, domain adaptation, and visual understanding. Strong programming skills (Python, PyTorch) and a solid foundation in ML/CV are essential.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="news">
            <h2>Recent News</h2>
            <div id="news-list">
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-date">November 2024</div>
                    <div>Our paper on few-shot learning was accepted to NeurIPS 2024!</div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-date">October 2024</div>
                    <div>I will be serving as an Area Chair for CVPR 2025.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-date">September 2024</div>
                    <div>Started a new position as Assistant Professor at University Name.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="news-item">
                    <div class="news-date">June 2024</div>
                    <div>Successfully defended my PhD thesis!</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="publications">
            <h2>Publications</h2>
            <div class="filter-buttons">
                <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterPublications('all')">All</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterPublications('highlighted')">Selected</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterPublications('2024')">2024</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterPublications('2023')">2023</button>
            </div>

            <div id="publications-list">
                <div class="publication highlighted" data-year="2024" data-highlighted="true">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Publication thumbnail" class="pub-image">
                    <div class="pub-content">
                        <div class="pub-title">
                            Learning to Generalize: Meta-Learning for Few-Shot Classification
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-authors">
                            <span class="me">Your Name</span>, Collaborator One, Collaborator Two, Advisor Name
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-venue">Neural Information Processing Systems (NeurIPS), 2024 <span class="award-text">(Best Paper Award)</span></div>
                        <div class="pub-links">
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Project Page</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Paper</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">arXiv</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Code</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">BibTeX</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="publication highlighted" data-year="2024" data-highlighted="true">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Publication thumbnail" class="pub-image">
                    <div class="pub-content">
                        <div class="pub-title">
                            Vision Transformers for Dense Prediction Tasks
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-authors">
                            Collaborator Three, <span class="me">Your Name</span>, Collaborator Four
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-venue">International Conference on Computer Vision (ICCV), 2024</div>
                        <div class="pub-links">
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Project Page</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Paper</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">arXiv</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Code</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">BibTeX</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="publication" data-year="2023" data-highlighted="false">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Publication thumbnail" class="pub-image">
                    <div class="pub-content">
                        <div class="pub-title">
                            Self-Supervised Learning for Visual Representations
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-authors">
                            <span class="me">Your Name</span>, Collaborator Five, Advisor Name
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-venue">Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR), 2023</div>
                        <div class="pub-links">
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Paper</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">arXiv</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Code</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">BibTeX</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="publication" data-year="2023" data-highlighted="false">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Publication thumbnail" class="pub-image">
                    <div class="pub-content">
                        <div class="pub-title">
                            Efficient Neural Architecture Search for Computer Vision
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-authors">
                            Collaborator Six, <span class="me">Your Name</span>, Collaborator Seven
                        </div>
                        <div class="pub-venue">International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML), 2023</div>
                        <div class="pub-links">
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Project Page</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Paper</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">Code</a>
                            <a href="#" class="pub-link">BibTeX</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="mentoring">
            <h2>Mentoring</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                I'm passionate about mentoring and have had the privilege of working with talented students on research projects.
            </p>
            
            <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-primary);">Current Mentees</h3>
                <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                    <p><strong>Undergraduate Student Name</strong> - Working on project about X (Fall 2024 - Present)</p>
                    <p><strong>Master's Student Name</strong> - Working on project about Y (Summer 2024 - Present)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-primary);">Past Mentees</h3>
                <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                    <p><strong>Former Student Name</strong> - Worked on project about Z (Spring 2024). Now at Company/School Name.</p>
                    <p><strong>Another Student Name</strong> - Worked on project about W (Fall 2023). Now at Company/School Name.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="teaching">
            <h2>Teaching</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                I have experience as a teaching assistant for the following courses:
            </p>
            
            <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                <p><strong>CS XXX: Introduction to Machine Learning</strong> - Teaching Assistant, Fall 2024<br>
                <span style="margin-left: 20px; font-size: 0.95em;">Held office hours, graded assignments, and developed course materials.</span></p>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>CS XXX: Computer Vision</strong> - Teaching Assistant, Spring 2024<br>
                <span style="margin-left: 20px; font-size: 0.95em;">Assisted with lectures, created homework problems, and mentored student projects.</span></p>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>CS XXX: Deep Learning</strong> - Teaching Assistant, Fall 2023<br>
                <span style="margin-left: 20px; font-size: 0.95em;">Led recitation sections and helped students with PyTorch implementations.</span></p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            © 2024 Your Name. Last updated: November 2024.
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script>
        function toggleProspective() {
            const content = document.getElementById('prospective-content');
            content.classList.toggle('show');
        }

        function filterPublications(filter) {
            const publications = document.querySelectorAll('.publication');
            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn');
            
            buttons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            event.target.classList.add('active');
            
            publications.forEach(pub => {
                if (filter === 'all') {
                    pub.style.display = 'flex';
                } else if (filter === 'highlighted') {
                    pub.style.display = pub.dataset.highlighted === 'true' ? 'flex' : 'none';
                } else {
                    pub.style.display = pub.dataset.year === filter ? 'flex' : 'none';
                }
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
